    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "凭借王子的不懈战斗和苏方的魔力引导，\\n众人终于彻底打倒了瓦尔法雷。\\n蓬莱小镇盛大地欢庆着春节，放起仙花焰。\\n王子一行人看着眼前的盛景，\\n细细品味着蓬莱小镇的美好。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "瓦尔法雷",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "好，苏方，快趁现在\\n排除瓦尔法雷周围的魔力！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "是！哈啊啊啊啊啊啊啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "瓦尔法雷",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你们回来啦……\\n瓦尔法雷怎么样了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "放心，它失去了所有力量，\\n终于倒下了……是我们赢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "龙之血的继承者啊，感谢你。\\n终于为这片土地带来了真正的和平。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "还有，蓬莱的孩子们啊……\\n多亏你们的力量才能成就这番伟业。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "哪、哪里的话……\\n您过奖了，徐福大人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "真是的，徐福你这家伙！\\n每次有什么好处都被你占了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "就因为这样，\\n人们才会只觉得你形象伟岸，\\n而老夫就是个滑稽老头。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "这是什么话，\\n你那滑稽老头的形象可不怪我。\\n反正你今年也要狂舞一番吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "哈哈哈！\\n那当然，今年除了庆祝新年，\\n还要庆祝成功击败宿敌呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "跳舞？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "对了，尤蒂尔\\n还不知道吧。蓬莱大人他……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "耳闻不如目见，\\n很快你就能看到了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "哈哈哈！\\n我们快回镇上，盛大地庆祝吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢噢！这就是仙花焰吗！真是不得了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "真的非常美丽……\\n就像是绽放在夜空中的花朵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "是啊，而且今年有些特殊，\\n毕竟也是庆祝成功守护了小镇。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我深有同感。\\n守护着要守护的事物时\\n观赏的仙花焰尤为美丽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "别这么容易满足啊！\\n我们换个地方吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "想更好地观赏仙花焰的话，\\n要找好距离和角度！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "跟我来这边，我会让你们看到\\n物理上和理论上最棒的仙花焰！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "哈哈哈！仙花焰固然精彩，\\n但老夫这边也值得一看哦～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "林佑",
            "context": "哇，蓬莱正扭着身子跳舞呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "这就是老夫引以为傲的龙之舞！\\n快看快看！我转！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢，这可真有魄力！\\n不错！再多转几圈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "哇！好厉害、好厉害！\\n蓬莱爷爷好帅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "毛毛",
            "context": "毛～毛～\\n（我也想跳啊～）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "林佑",
            "context": "啊哈哈！\\n好久没庆祝春节了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "大家都乐在其中……\\n来到这个小镇真是太好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢谢你，苏方。\\n你让我们看到了最棒的仙花焰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我才要道谢呢。\\n这一切都是多亏你们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "其实我……对父亲的话耿耿于怀。\\n我一直在思考对仙花焰来说\\n最重要的东西到底是什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我一直执着于华丽的色彩和效果。\\n但是，我看着各位，\\n才发现自己错了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "看着我们？\\n我对仙花焰可是一无所知啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "各位都拥有很强的实力，\\n却从不有意夸耀自己，\\n只是为了守护人们的笑容而战。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "看到这些，我终于明白了父亲的话。\\n仙花焰最重要的\\n就是观赏仙花焰的人的笑容。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "所以，我能做出最棒的仙花焰\\n也是多亏了各位。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来是这样……\\n很高兴能帮上你的忙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "看来你父亲作为仙花焰的制作者\\n已经远远超越了我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "徐福大人？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "对我而言，\\n仙花焰只不过是教授镇上的人们\\n操纵魔力的手段罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "这就相当于在欺骗你们，\\n与人们的笑容背道而驰。\\n我不是一位合格的仙花焰制作者。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "哪有……要是没有徐福大人的深谋远虑，\\n这座小镇就要惨遭瓦尔法雷蹂躏了。\\n您根本不用道歉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。要是没有你，小镇就会被毁，\\n人们也没法再露出笑容。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也就是说，你也是在\\n为了人们的笑容而制作仙花焰，\\n难道不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "不管徐福大人怎么想，\\n镇上的人们看到徐福大人的仙花焰后，\\n都欣喜地露出了笑容。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我也是……失去父母时看到的\\n仙花焰的美丽，我绝不会忘记。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "大家一直都很期待。\\n今年也请让我们见识一下\\n徐福大人的仙花焰！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "好吧……这是真心诚意\\n只为大家的笑容而放的仙花焰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "镇上的人",
            "context": "啊！那是徐福大人的仙花焰！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "镇上的人",
            "context": "徐福大人！欢迎回来！\\n我们一直在等您呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "这座镇上的人们和100年前一样……\\n还是会这样迎接我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "以前我对此没有什么特别的感触，\\n但不知从何时起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "我开始……\\n为人们的迎接和款待而高兴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "徐福大人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "我们麒麟族因为拥有特殊能力\\n而选择了隐居，远离尘世。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "但不可思议的是，每到这个时间，\\n我都会想要回到这里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我似乎……\\n能明白徐福大人的感受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我想那是因为……这座小镇就是故乡，\\n这里有等待自己归来的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "故乡、吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "原来如此……也许是吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_08_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "就这样，春节夜色渐深……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "回到故乡的人、等待他人归来的人，\\n都各自品味着属于自己的幸福……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}